  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A three-cornered battle for the position of president?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Parliamentary sources state that three names have been proposed for the presidency.",
        "The names of Prime Minister Ranil Wickramasinghe, Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna Member of Parliament Dallas Alahapperuma and Opposition Leader Sajith Premadasa have been proposed.",
        "The secret ballot of the Parliament to elect the new President will be held on July 20.",
        "However, the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has not been officially announced until now."
      ],
